<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-RUSSIA-PUTIN-REVIEW-2NDTAKE-NYT </SLUG>
  
 MOSCOW: introduced early.  
<TEXT>
<P>
   6. PUBLIC HEALTH _ Russia is a sick country, its social safety
