<HEADLINE>
PINOCHET'S REVENGE: OLIVER NORTH, YOU'D BETTER WATCH OUT 
</HEADLINE>
   (The Week in Review)  
 (NOTE TO INTERNATIONAL CLIENTS: For international clients' use by
