<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-25 17:00 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7911 &Cx1f; taf-z
u s BC-GLF-TPC-NYT &LR;      03-25 0683
