17th tee, they'll be dealing with more than the wind, water and
sand. Add another natural hazard to the game and to The Players
Championship's island hole: The fans. No longer do they applaud
good shots and quietly shake their heads at bad ones. Now golf fans
boo, jeer, harass, heckle and even confront players as if this were
a WWF card. (Dolch, Palm Beach Post). 21.
