<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-25 18:54 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7974 &Cx1f; taf-z
u f BC-AT-HOME-REAL-865&AMP;ADD-     03-25 1139
