<DOCNO> NYT20000325.0210 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-25 21:09 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8031 &Cx1f; kan-z
r f BC-MOVIE-TECH-KAN &LR;      03-25 1360
