Kevin Johnson's tottering legs turn to jelly after a few trips up
and down the hardwood at America West Arena? Don't worry, the Suns'
soothsaying boss, Jerry Colangelo, is way behind you. Story will
move in the ``A'' and ``K'' categories.  &QL;
